---
title: "Inclement Weather Warning: January 2026"
---

<h1><span class="eng">Inclement Weather Warning: January 2026</span><span class="chn">2026年1月的极端天气警告</span></h1>


<span class="eng">According to the recent weather forcast, there will be a severe winter weather in the upcoming weekend (from January 23, 2026). The Bear Resort thereby suggest everyone to take on the following actions and reminders.</span>
<span class="chn">依据最新天气预报，极端冬日天气将在本周末（2026年1月23日起）袭来。小熊樂園建议大家进行以下防备。</span>

![No Travel](/inc-weather/do-not-travel.png)
<h2><span class="eng">Avoid Traveling during the Weather</span><span class="chn">避免在雪天出行</span></h2>

![Keep Charged](/inc-weather/keep-charged.png)
<h2><span class="eng">Keep Important Devices Charged (Phones, Power Banks, and Flashlights)</span><span class="chn">将重要设备充电（手机、充电宝、手电筒）</span></h2>

![Store Food](/inc-weather/store-food.png)
<h2><span class="eng">Prepare Enough Food before the Snow</span><span class="chn">在雪天前准备充足食物</span></h2>

![Call Emergency](/inc-weather/call-emergency.png)
<h2><span class="eng">Call for Help during Emergency</span><span class="chn">在紧急情况下拨打电话求助</span></h2>

<span class="eng">We hope everyone can survive the upcoming winter weather. Keep warm, keep safe.</span>
<span class="chn">我们希望大家安稳地度过本次大雪。保持温暖，保持安全！</span>
